creator: Various
description:
LibriVox recording of Short Poetry Collection 153 by Various.
Read in English by Shakira Searle; Ian King; Bruce Kachuk; John Burlinson; VfkaBT; Phil Chenevert; Sonia; Ryan Finch; Tony Addison; Newgatenovelist; Douglas Thornton; Algy Pug; Son of the Exiles
This is a collection of 29 poems read by LibriVox volunteers for February 2016. It includes: Absence, by Amy Lowell The Coming of the End, by Thomas Hardy Afterwards, by Thomas Hardy The Day Of Days, by William Morris The Cheat of Cupid. Or, The Ungentle Guest, by Robert Herrick Fascination, by John B. Tabb Fie, Foolish Earth, by Fulke Greville Forty-Second Street, by Emmy Veronica Sanders The Hound of Heaven, by Francis Thompson An Hymn to Humanity, by Phillis Wheatley In the Wilderness, by Robert Graves Kitty, a fair but frozen maid, by David Garrick Lochinvar, by Sir Walter Scott Marriage Thoughts: By Morsellin Khan, by Laurence Hope New Orleans, by Lola Ridge No Master, by William Morris Ode to Evening, by William Collins Ode 1.5 (Quis Multa Gracilis), by Quintus Horatius Flaccus (Horace) The Open Steeplechase, by Andrew Barton Paterson Ozymandias of Egypt, by Percy Bysshe Shelley Reminiscence of Mahomed Akram, by Laurence Hope The River Merchant's Wife, by Bai Li 李白 Song, by Thomas Moore Song of the Chattahoochee, by Sidney Lanier Story by Lalla-ji, the Priest, by Laurence Hope The Swimmer, by Adam Lindsay Gordon Till All the Bad Things Came Untrue, by Henry Lawson To The Muse Of The North, by William Morris The Troubadour, by W. S. Gilbert For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
